VK,is,a,popular,European,social,networking,website,The,VK,Merchant,API,it,offers,provides,a,means,of,connecting,applications,and,external,internet,stores,to,the,VK,payment,system,This,allows,buyers,to,pay,for,items,and,services,in,an,internet,store,from,their,personal,VK,account,One,unique,feature,of,the,VK,payment,system,is,that,it,allows,users,to,chip,in,together,on,purchases,with,their,friends